{"word":"H8032 - שִׁלְשֹׁום - shilshôwm - shil-shome' - Before","slug":"H8032","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שִׁלְשֹׁום</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shilshôwm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shil-shome'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Before"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DD;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D5;&#x05DD; - shilsho&#x0302;m  shilsho&#x0302;m</b> - <i>shil-shome', shil-shome'</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/H8028\">H8028</a>; <i>trebly</i>, that is, (in time) <i>day before yesterday: - </i> + before (that time, -time), excellent things [from the margin], + heretofore, three days, + time past."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7597\">H7597</a>, <a href=\"#/H7969\">H7969</a>, <a href=\"#/H7970\">H7970</a>, <a href=\"#/H7991\">H7991</a>, <a href=\"#/H7992\">H7992</a>, <a href=\"#/H8027\">H8027</a>, <a href=\"#/H8028\">H8028</a>, <a href=\"#/H8029\">H8029</a>, <a href=\"#/H8030\">H8030</a>, <a href=\"#/H8031\">H8031</a>"}]}